  <name>File Shredder</name>
  <summary>Permanently delete your files</summary>
  <description>
    <p>File Shredder is a file deletion program for the GNOME desktop environment. It
      is designed to permanently remove sensitive files from your computer, enhancing
      data privacy.
		</p>
		<p>Within a certain limit, it is effective. However, modern SSDs use certain technologies
		  to extend its lifetime, which has the side effect of ensuring that shredding is never
		  perfect, and no software can fix that. But shredding significantly increases the
		  difficulty of data recovery since it requires specialized software and hardware.
		</p>
  </description>
